[
  {
    "text": "What the...",
    "start": 16.015,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "(FUNK MUSIC STOPS)",
    "start": 18.56,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "(FUNK MUSIC RESUMES)",
    "start": 21.062,
    "duration": 1.043
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey!",
    "start": 22.188,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "(DOOR BELL RINGS)",
    "start": 36.453,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "Tim, look who's here.",
    "start": 42.25,
    "duration": 1.627
  },
  {
    "text": "Meet your new baby brother.",
    "start": 46.629,
    "duration": 4.421
  },
  {
    "text": "Baby what?",
    "start": 51.217,
    "duration": 1.085
  },
  {
    "text": "Brother.",
    "start": 52.469,
    "duration": 3.294
  },
  {
    "text": "ADULT TIM:\nI had a million questions.",
    "start": 55.93,
    "duration": 1.794
  },
  {
    "text": "Who is this guy?\nWhy is he here?",
    "start": 57.891,
    "duration": 1.835
  },
  {
    "text": "What's with that outfit?",
    "start": 59.893,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "Why's he so fat?\nWhy's he staring at me?",
    "start": 61.06,
    "duration": 2.253
  },
  {
    "text": "Does he know karate?\nWhat's going on?",
    "start": 63.48,
    "duration": 1.835
  },
  {
    "text": "(CRYING)",
    "start": 65.899,
    "duration": 1.209
  },
  {
    "text": "That way?",
    "start": 67.233,
    "duration": 0.834
  },
  {
    "text": "DAD: Okay.\nMOM: Okay.",
    "start": 68.234,
    "duration": 0.876
  },
  {
    "text": "Right from the start,\nhe was yelling at people...",
    "start": 69.277,
    "duration": 1.543
  },
  {
    "text": "ordering everyone around.\n(CONTINUES CRYING)",
    "start": 70.987,
    "duration": 1.668
  },
  {
    "text": "MOM: Oh, you want this?",
    "start": 72.822,
    "duration": 1.585
  },
  {
    "text": "One thing was clear.\nHe was the boss.",
    "start": 74.949,
    "duration": 3.295
  },
  {
    "text": "He set up his office,\nright smack dab in\nthe middle of the house.",
    "start": 78.828,
    "duration": 2.67
  },
  {
    "text": "(CRYING)",
    "start": 81.581,
    "duration": 1.376
  },
  {
    "text": "He conducted meetings.",
    "start": 83.416,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "You called?\nDo you need Sefior Squeaky?",
    "start": 84.584,
    "duration": 1.835
  },
  {
    "text": "(BOSS BABY CONTINUES CRYING)\nHey!",
    "start": 86.961,
    "duration": 1.669
  },
  {
    "text": "Lots and lots of meetings.\nWhoa!",
    "start": 88.755,
    "duration": 2.169
  },
  {
    "text": "Even in\nthe middle of the night.",
    "start": 91.09,
    "duration": 1.669
  },
  {
    "text": "(BOSS BABY CRYING)",
    "start": 93.009,
    "duration": 1.251
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm up! I'm up!",
    "start": 94.594,
    "duration": 1.418
  },
  {
    "text": "We're coming!\nWe'll be right there!",
    "start": 96.179,
    "duration": 1.418
  },
  {
    "text": "If things weren't done\nto his immediate\nsatisfaction...",
    "start": 97.764,
    "duration": 3.211
  },
  {
    "text": "he had a fit.",
    "start": 102.435,
    "duration": 2.085
  },
  {
    "text": "(HUFFING)",
    "start": 104.604,
    "duration": 2.002
  },
  {
    "text": "(CRYING LOUDLY)",
    "start": 108.65,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "Argh!",
    "start": 109.776,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "DAD: Where's the bottle?\nHe has to have his bottle!",
    "start": 110.86,
    "duration": 2.753
  },
  {
    "text": "He had everyone wrapped around\nhis chubby little finger.",
    "start": 113.78,
    "duration": 2.752
  },
  {
    "text": "La la la!",
    "start": 116.783,
    "duration": 1.251
  },
  {
    "text": "Everyone except for me.",
    "start": 118.117,
    "duration": 2.002
  },
  {
    "text": "DAD: Diaper!\nMOM: Bottle!",
    "start": 120.453,
    "duration": 1.043
  },
  {
    "text": "DAD: Diaper!\nMOM: Bottle!",
    "start": 121.579,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "Dad! I can't sleep.",
    "start": 122.997,
    "duration": 1.961
  },
  {
    "text": "I know, bud. Me neither.",
    "start": 125.124,
    "duration": 1.502
  },
  {
    "text": "The baby needs a lot\nof attention right now.",
    "start": 126.793,
    "duration": 1.751
  },
  {
    "text": "(BOSS BABY CRYING)\nOkay, good talk!",
    "start": 128.628,
    "duration": 1.418
  },
  {
    "text": "But...\nDAD: It's okay.",
    "start": 130.213,
    "duration": 1.126
  },
  {
    "text": "Daddy's here. Daddy's here.",
    "start": 131.506,
    "duration": 1.126
  },
  {
    "text": "What about me?",
    "start": 135.009,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "The year: 2057.",
    "start": 137.637,
    "duration": 1.918
  },
  {
    "text": "Ensign T-Rex and I\nare investigating\na hostile alien invasion.",
    "start": 139.722,
    "duration": 4.296
  },
  {
    "text": "(WHIMPERS)",
    "start": 146.145,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "Whoa! Ah!",
    "start": 160.159,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "It's so much worse\nthan we thought.",
    "start": 167.166,
    "duration": 2.002
  },
  {
    "text": "(ROARS)",
    "start": 169.252,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "(MUFFLED SCREAM)",
    "start": 178.845,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "Mom, he's naked!",
    "start": 180.221,
    "duration": 1.21
  },
  {
    "text": "(CHUCKLES)",
    "start": 181.514,
    "duration": 1.21
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm naked!\n(LAUGHS)",
    "start": 182.849,
    "duration": 1.084
  },
  {
    "text": "DAD: Say \"naked.\"",
    "start": 184.017,
    "duration": 1.084
  },
  {
    "text": "No!",
    "start": 185.268,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm making great progress\nwith the parents already.",
    "start": 189.188,
    "duration": 2.837
  },
  {
    "text": "The usual procedure,\nsleep deprivation,\nhunger strikes.",
    "start": 192.191,
    "duration": 4.338
  },
  {
    "text": "They're very disoriented.",
    "start": 196.696,
    "duration": 1.668
  },
  {
    "text": "(CHUCKLING) I've got them\neating out of the\npalm of my hand.",
    "start": 198.531,
    "duration": 2.419
  },
  {
    "text": "They do everything for me.",
    "start": 201.117,
    "duration": 2.252
  },
  {
    "text": "It's hilarious.",
    "start": 203.536,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "But I think the kid\nmight be on to me.",
    "start": 204.871,
    "duration": 1.585
  },
  {
    "text": "No, I can handle him.",
    "start": 207.248,
    "duration": 2.127
  },
  {
    "text": "I know how important\nthis mission is\nto the company.",
    "start": 209.542,
    "duration": 2.211
  },
  {
    "text": "Mission?",
    "start": 211.919,
    "duration": 1.21
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, trust me, ma'am.\nYou got the right baby\nfor this job.",
    "start": 213.296,
    "duration": 2.836
  },
  {
    "text": "Hands up, devil baby!",
    "start": 216.299,
    "duration": 1.418
  },
  {
    "text": "Fart! Poop! Doodie!",
    "start": 217.884,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "(YELLING AND EXCLAIMING)",
    "start": 219.051,
    "duration": 2.044
  },
  {
    "text": "I've gotta deal\nwith the k-i-d.",
    "start": 222.472,
    "duration": 1.501
  },
  {
    "text": "You can talk!",
    "start": 224.14,
    "duration": 0.959
  },
  {
    "text": "Uh, goo-goo ga-ga.",
    "start": 225.558,
    "duration": 2.002
  },
  {
    "text": "No, you can really talk.\nI heard you!",
    "start": 227.727,
    "duration": 2.252
  },
  {
    "text": "Fine. I can talk.",
    "start": 230.98,
    "duration": 2.085
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, let's see\nif you can listen.",
    "start": 233.232,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "Get me a double espresso...",
    "start": 234.567,
    "duration": 1.084
  },
  {
    "text": "and see if there's someplace\naround here with decent sushi.",
    "start": 235.818,
    "duration": 1.919
  },
  {
    "text": "I'd Kill\nfor a spicy tuna roll\nright about now.",
    "start": 237.904,
    "duration": 3.086
  },
  {
    "text": "Get yourself\na little something.",
    "start": 241.157,
    "duration": 1.585
  },
  {
    "text": "Who are you?",
    "start": 242.909,
    "duration": 1.501
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's just say I'm the boss.",
    "start": 244.577,
    "duration": 3.587
  },
  {
    "text": "The boss? You're a baby!\nYou wear a diaper.",
    "start": 248.331,
    "duration": 3.253
  },
  {
    "text": "You know who else\nwears diapers?",
    "start": 251.751,
    "duration": 1.585
  },
  {
    "text": "Astronauts and NASCAR drivers,\nthat's who.",
    "start": 253.503,
    "duration": 2.419
  },
  {
    "text": "It's called efficiency,\nTempleton.",
    "start": 256.088,
    "duration": 1.377
  },
  {
    "text": "The average\ntoddler spends, what?",
    "start": 257.632,
    "duration": 1.71
  },
  {
    "text": "45 hours a year on the potty?",
    "start": 259.425,
    "duration": 2.002
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm the boss. (LAUGHING)",
    "start": 261.594,
    "duration": 1.543
  },
  {
    "text": "I don't have\nthat kind of spare time.",
    "start": 263.262,
    "duration": 1.669
  },
  {
    "text": "Well,\nyou're not the boss of me.",
    "start": 265.097,
    "duration": 1.544
  },
  {
    "text": "I am the boss of you.",
    "start": 266.807,
    "duration": 1.043
  },
  {
    "text": "No, you're not.",
    "start": 267.934,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "Am, too.\nAre not.",
    "start": 269.101,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "Am, too!\nAre not!",
    "start": 270.269,
    "duration": 1.252
  },
  {
    "text": "Am, too.\nAre not!",
    "start": 272.104,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "(OVER RECORDING) Am, too.\nAre not!",
    "start": 273.439,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "Am, too. Am, too.",
    "start": 274.607,
    "duration": 1.251
  },
  {
    "text": "Am, too. Am, too.",
    "start": 276.025,
    "duration": 1.084
  },
  {
    "text": "I was here first.",
    "start": 277.276,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "Just wait until Mom and Dad\nfind out about this.",
    "start": 278.444,
    "duration": 2.086
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, yeah? You think\nthey'd pick you over me?",
    "start": 280.696,
    "duration": 2.336
  },
  {
    "text": "With your track record?",
    "start": 283.199,
    "duration": 1.501
  },
  {
    "text": "You don't know\nanything about me.",
    "start": 284.867,
    "duration": 1.585
  },
  {
    "text": "So that's how you wanna\nplay it, huh? Let's see.",
    "start": 287.954,
    "duration": 2.419
  },
  {
    "text": "Templeton, Timothy.\nMiddle name....",
    "start": 290.998,
    "duration": 2.169
  },
  {
    "text": "(LAUGHS)",
    "start": 293.292,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm sorry. Leslie!",
    "start": 295.127,
    "duration": 1.836
  },
  {
    "text": "Mostly C's...\nHow do you know all that?",
    "start": 297.129,
    "duration": 1.71
  },
  {
    "text": "Can't ride a bike\nwithout training wheels?",
    "start": 299.006,
    "duration": 2.127
  },
  {
    "text": "Even bears can ride a bike\nwithout training wheels,\nLeslie.",
    "start": 301.3,
    "duration": 4.004
  },
  {
    "text": "Um...\nDOB says you're seven.",
    "start": 305.471,
    "duration": 1.752
  },
  {
    "text": "Seven and a half.",
    "start": 307.39,
    "duration": 1.209
  },
  {
    "text": "(SNORING)",
    "start": 308.683,
    "duration": 1.167
  },
  {
    "text": "Power nap!\nUh, you were saying?",
    "start": 310.518,
    "duration": 2.002
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm seven and a half.",
    "start": 312.687,
    "duration": 1.459
  },
  {
    "text": "Exactly! You're old.",
    "start": 314.313,
    "duration": 1.502
  },
  {
    "text": "It's time to make way\nfor the next generation.",
    "start": 315.982,
    "duration": 2.919
  },
  {
    "text": "It's the way of the world.",
    "start": 319.068,
    "duration": 1.251
  },
  {
    "text": "You would never ask\nyour parents for an old toy.",
    "start": 320.486,
    "duration": 2.252
  },
  {
    "text": "Lam-Lam?",
    "start": 322.905,
    "duration": 0.918
  },
  {
    "text": "Everyone wants\nthe hot, new thing.",
    "start": 323.99,
    "duration": 1.042
  },
  {
    "text": "ROBOT: Destroy. Destroy.",
    "start": 325.199,
    "duration": 1.502
  },
  {
    "text": "Lam-Lam!",
    "start": 326.867,
    "duration": 1.043
  },
  {
    "text": "I've got fresh batteries.",
    "start": 327.994,
    "duration": 1.334
  },
  {
    "text": "Boom!",
    "start": 329.495,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "Mom and Dad\ndon't even know you.",
    "start": 330.663,
    "duration": 1.585
  },
  {
    "text": "They love me!",
    "start": 332.415,
    "duration": 1.293
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, yeah? Do the math, kid.",
    "start": 333.874,
    "duration": 1.46
  },
  {
    "text": "There's only\nso much love to go around.",
    "start": 335.501,
    "duration": 2.377
  },
  {
    "text": "It's like these beads.",
    "start": 338.045,
    "duration": 1.877
  },
  {
    "text": "You used to have\nall your parents' love.",
    "start": 340.089,
    "duration": 2.419
  },
  {
    "text": "All their time.\nAll their attention.",
    "start": 342.675,
    "duration": 2.252
  },
  {
    "text": "You had all the beads.",
    "start": 345.094,
    "duration": 2.085
  },
  {
    "text": "But then I came along.",
    "start": 347.346,
    "duration": 1.543
  },
  {
    "text": "Babies take up a lot of time.",
    "start": 349.056,
    "duration": 1.877
  },
  {
    "text": "They need a lot of attention.\nThey get all the love.",
    "start": 351.1,
    "duration": 3.42
  },
  {
    "text": "We could share.",
    "start": 355.062,
    "duration": 1.293
  },
  {
    "text": "You obviously didn't\ngo to business school.",
    "start": 356.522,
    "duration": 2.252
  },
  {
    "text": "Look, Templeton,\nthe numbers just don't add up.",
    "start": 362.695,
    "duration": 3.211
  },
  {
    "text": "There's not enough love\nfor the two of us.",
    "start": 366.073,
    "duration": 2.294
  },
  {
    "text": "Not enough beads\nto go around.",
    "start": 368.534,
    "duration": 2.169
  },
  {
    "text": "And then,\nall of a sudden, (GASPS)",
    "start": 370.87,
    "duration": 2.252
  },
  {
    "text": "there's no place for Tim.",
    "start": 373.205,
    "duration": 1.252
  },
  {
    "text": "Tim doesn't fit anymore.",
    "start": 374.623,
    "duration": 1.502
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, no!\nWhat about Tim? (CACKLES)",
    "start": 376.292,
    "duration": 3.253
  },
  {
    "text": "So keep quiet.\nStay out of my way.",
    "start": 382.965,
    "duration": 2.336
  },
  {
    "text": "Or there's gonna be cutbacks.",
    "start": 385.468,
    "duration": 1.501
  },
  {
    "text": "Binky. Papish. Nuk-Nuk.",
    "start": 388.387,
    "duration": 2.67
  },
  {
    "text": "Boo-Boo. Bo-Bo. Bah-Bah.",
    "start": 391.223,
    "duration": 2.211
  },
  {
    "text": "Chupie. Hushie-Baby. Tootsie.",
    "start": 393.601,
    "duration": 2.294
  },
  {
    "text": "It goes by many names.",
    "start": 396.062,
    "duration": 2.043
  },
  {
    "text": "But through its power,\nyou will know the truth.",
    "start": 398.272,
    "duration": 2.961
  },
  {
    "text": "Come on, faster!",
    "start": 408.24,
    "duration": 0.918
  },
  {
    "text": "(YELLING)",
    "start": 413.12,
    "duration": 2.127
  },
  {
    "text": "Mommy!",
    "start": 416.499,
    "duration": 0.834
  },
  {
    "text": "(GRUNTS)",
    "start": 425.633,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "Where are we?",
    "start": 431.18,
    "duration": 1.251
  },
  {
    "text": "Welcome to Baby Corp!",
    "start": 432.598,
    "duration": 2.336
  },
  {
    "text": "Whoa!",
    "start": 437.77,
    "duration": 1.043
  },
  {
    "text": "(BLOWS WHISTLE)\n(INDISTINCT CHATTERING)",
    "start": 439.104,
    "duration": 1.961
  },
  {
    "text": "No way.",
    "start": 441.148,
    "duration": 1.21
  },
  {
    "text": "(CRIES)",
    "start": 443.317,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you.\nTIM: What?",
    "start": 444.527,
    "duration": 1.084
  },
  {
    "text": "(THANKING IN ITALIAN)",
    "start": 445.694,
    "duration": 0.918
  },
  {
    "text": "Relax.\nThey can't see us or hear us.",
    "start": 447.696,
    "duration": 2.253
  },
  {
    "text": "We're, like,\nvirtual and stuff?",
    "start": 450.115,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "Yep.",
    "start": 451.367,
    "duration": 0.834
  },
  {
    "text": "You mean they won't feel this?",
    "start": 452.284,
    "duration": 1.043
  },
  {
    "text": "Nope. Nada.\nOr this?",
    "start": 453.452,
    "duration": 1.668
  },
  {
    "text": "Karate!",
    "start": 455.287,
    "duration": 0.918
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't embarrass yourself,\nTempleton.",
    "start": 457.54,
    "duration": 1.376
  },
  {
    "text": "I can still see you.",
    "start": 458.999,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "TIM: So this is\nwhere babies come from?",
    "start": 460.167,
    "duration": 1.877
  },
  {
    "text": "BOSS BABY: Where'd you think,\nthe cabbage patch?",
    "start": 462.211,
    "duration": 2.127
  },
  {
    "text": "Magic fairies?",
    "start": 464.505,
    "duration": 0.959
  },
  {
    "text": "No, my parents told me that...",
    "start": 465.631,
    "duration": 2.002
  },
  {
    "text": "(INDISTINCT WHISPERING)",
    "start": 467.716,
    "duration": 1.043
  },
  {
    "text": "What?",
    "start": 468.843,
    "duration": 1.167
  },
  {
    "text": "Ugh, no. That's disgusting.",
    "start": 470.177,
    "duration": 2.044
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, it didn't sound\nright to me, either.",
    "start": 472.388,
    "duration": 2.252
  },
  {
    "text": "I can't believe my parents\ndidn't tell me about this.",
    "start": 475.558,
    "duration": 2.293
  },
  {
    "text": "If people knew\nwhere babies really came from,",
    "start": 478.018,
    "duration": 2.002
  },
  {
    "text": "they'd never have one.",
    "start": 480.145,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "Same thing with\nhot dogs, by the way.",
    "start": 481.48,
    "duration": 1.71
  },
  {
    "text": "FEMALE AUTOMATED VOICE:\nGoing upsies! (CHUCKLES)",
    "start": 483.357,
    "duration": 1.376
  },
  {
    "text": "TIM: So how come\nI don't remember this place?",
    "start": 486.151,
    "duration": 1.669
  },
  {
    "text": "BOSS BABY: Oh, you did.",
    "start": 487.987,
    "duration": 0.834
  },
  {
    "text": "But after normal babies\nget their\npacifiers taken away...",
    "start": 488.988,
    "duration": 2.252
  },
  {
    "text": "you forget\nall about Baby Corp.",
    "start": 491.407,
    "duration": 1.918
  },
  {
    "text": "How come you're not normal?",
    "start": 493.492,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "A few of us,\nthe best of the best...",
    "start": 494.994,
    "duration": 2.21
  },
  {
    "text": "are selected for the...",
    "start": 497.371,
    "duration": 1.627
  },
  {
    "text": "Who-hoo!",
    "start": 499.248,
    "duration": 1.668
  },
  {
    "text": "For the ultimate honor.",
    "start": 501.667,
    "duration": 1.752
  },
  {
    "text": "Upper management.",
    "start": 504.378,
    "duration": 1.627
  },
  {
    "text": "This, Templeton,\nis where all the action is.",
    "start": 506.171,
    "duration": 3.504
  },
  {
    "text": "FEMALE AUTOMATED VOICE:\nNap time in Sector G.",
    "start": 509.842,
    "duration": 2.335
  },
  {
    "text": "So this whole\nplace is run by babies?",
    "start": 512.928,
    "duration": 1.835
  },
  {
    "text": "Yep.",
    "start": 514.93,
    "duration": 0.918
  },
  {
    "text": "My Dad says,\n\"Those who can, do.\"",
    "start": 516.015,
    "duration": 2.168
  },
  {
    "text": "\"And those who can't,\nsupervise.\"",
    "start": 518.35,
    "duration": 1.418
  },
  {
    "text": "Your father is a hippie.",
    "start": 520.019,
    "duration": 1.251
  },
  {
    "text": "(CRYING)",
    "start": 521.854,
    "duration": 1.042
  },
  {
    "text": "What happens\nwhen you grow up?",
    "start": 523.022,
    "duration": 1.376
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, we don't.",
    "start": 524.565,
    "duration": 0.834
  },
  {
    "text": "We drink\na super-secret baby formula\nthat keeps us babies forever.",
    "start": 525.566,
    "duration": 3.295
  },
  {
    "text": "(ALL BURPING)",
    "start": 528.944,
    "duration": 1.668
  },
  {
    "text": "Back to work!\nFormula break is over!",
    "start": 530.696,
    "duration": 2.502
  },
  {
    "text": "We're in a crisis here!\n(RINGS)",
    "start": 533.365,
    "duration": 1.418
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't you know\nwe're in a crisis here?",
    "start": 534.95,
    "duration": 1.502
  },
  {
    "text": "Who is that?",
    "start": 536.618,
    "duration": 0.918
  },
  {
    "text": "That is my boss.\nBig Boss Baby.",
    "start": 537.703,
    "duration": 2.544
  },
  {
    "text": "What is she screaming about?",
    "start": 540.414,
    "duration": 1.96
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, see this pie chart?",
    "start": 542.541,
    "duration": 1.418
  },
  {
    "text": "Wow,\nit looks like a giant pie.",
    "start": 544.376,
    "duration": 2.044
  },
  {
    "text": "It represents all the love\nthere is in the world.",
    "start": 546.587,
    "duration": 2.461
  },
  {
    "text": "I love pie.\nWho doesn't?",
    "start": 549.214,
    "duration": 1.252
  },
  {
    "text": "Apple.\nFine.",
    "start": 550.632,
    "duration": 0.835
  },
  {
    "text": "No, cherry!\nPerfect!",
    "start": 551.633,
    "duration": 0.918
  },
  {
    "text": "Not pumpkin.\nOkay.",
    "start": 552.718,
    "duration": 0.876
  },
  {
    "text": "That's a vegetable.",
    "start": 553.761,
    "duration": 0.792
  },
  {
    "text": "Point is, the puppies' slice\nis getting bigger and bigger.",
    "start": 554.72,
    "duration": 3.378
  },
  {
    "text": "(BABY CRYING)",
    "start": 558.223,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "They're stealing\nall our love!",
    "start": 559.433,
    "duration": 1.627
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, just like\nyou did to me.",
    "start": 561.226,
    "duration": 2.002
  },
  {
    "text": "Exactly.",
    "start": 563.395,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh!\nAnd if this keeps up...",
    "start": 564.563,
    "duration": 2.002
  },
  {
    "text": "there might not be enough pie\nleft for babies.",
    "start": 566.732,
    "duration": 2.544
  },
  {
    "text": "No pie?",
    "start": 569.443,
    "duration": 0.959
  },
  {
    "text": "No pie.",
    "start": 570.569,
    "duration": 1.668
  },
  {
    "text": "[robot nurse]\nDon't cry. There, there.",
    "start": 579.703,
    "duration": 1.835
  },
  {
    "text": "All better.",
    "start": 581.622,
    "duration": 1.042
  },
  {
    "text": "[grunting]",
    "start": 582.748,
    "duration": 2.377
  },
  {
    "text": "[grunts, mutters]",
    "start": 586.335,
    "duration": 1.668
  },
  {
    "text": "[spits]",
    "start": 589.588,
    "duration": 1.668
  },
  {
    "text": "[sighs] It's like they always say.",
    "start": 592.8,
    "duration": 2.585
  },
  {
    "text": "If you want something done right,",
    "start": 595.469,
    "duration": 1.752
  },
  {
    "text": "you have to do it without your brother.",
    "start": 597.304,
    "duration": 1.96
  },
  {
    "text": "We meet again, doorknob.",
    "start": 600.432,
    "duration": 2.544
  },
  {
    "text": "[grunting]",
    "start": 604.895,
    "duration": 1.501
  },
  {
    "text": "[door opens, creaks]",
    "start": 606.48,
    "duration": 1.752
  },
  {
    "text": "Hello. Welcome, welcome.",
    "start": 609.691,
    "duration": 2.962
  },
  {
    "text": "Please, come in. Enfrez-vous.",
    "start": 612.736,
    "duration": 2.294
  },
  {
    "text": "- You're here.\n- Oh, yes.",
    "start": 615.114,
    "duration": 1.543
  },
  {
    "text": "I-- I was expecting you.",
    "start": 616.74,
    "duration": 2.544
  },
  {
    "text": "I-- [grunts]",
    "start": 621.036,
    "duration": 1.502
  },
  {
    "text": "[beeps]",
    "start": 622.621,
    "duration": 0.959
  },
  {
    "text": "I expected that you...",
    "start": 624.248,
    "duration": 1.585
  },
  {
    "text": "would be... expecting me.",
    "start": 625.916,
    "duration": 2.085
  },
  {
    "text": "So there.",
    "start": 628.085,
    "duration": 1.042
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, and by the way,\nI know why you're here.",
    "start": 629.211,
    "duration": 3.67
  },
  {
    "text": "- So... so there.\n- [beeps]",
    "start": 632.965,
    "duration": 1.668
  },
  {
    "text": "- [door locks]\n- [chuckles]",
    "start": 634.716,
    "duration": 1.502
  },
  {
    "text": "You do?",
    "start": 636.301,
    "duration": 1.043
  },
  {
    "text": "Mm-hmm. Yes, I do.",
    "start": 637.427,
    "duration": 2.336
  },
  {
    "text": "- Have a seat, please.\n- [grunts] Thank you.",
    "start": 640.597,
    "duration": 2.336
  },
  {
    "text": "- [Erwin] You know what you are?\n- Mmm?",
    "start": 643.016,
    "duration": 1.544
  },
  {
    "text": "You are, if I may, extremely intelligent.",
    "start": 644.643,
    "duration": 4.171
  },
  {
    "text": "Go on.",
    "start": 648.897,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "As a matter of fact,\nI've been observing you.",
    "start": 649.982,
    "duration": 2.961
  },
  {
    "text": "Spends time wisely, check.",
    "start": 653.026,
    "duration": 2.336
  },
  {
    "text": "Makes good use\nof classroom materials, check.",
    "start": 655.445,
    "duration": 2.461
  },
  {
    "text": "Keeps hands to self, check.",
    "start": 657.99,
    "duration": 1.96
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey, forget \"works well with others.\"",
    "start": 660.033,
    "duration": 2.086
  },
  {
    "text": "You make others work well for you.",
    "start": 662.202,
    "duration": 3.003
  },
  {
    "text": "That's literally the title\nof the book I'm working on.",
    "start": 665.289,
    "duration": 3.253
  },
  {
    "text": "No kidding.",
    "start": 668.625,
    "duration": 0.918
  },
  {
    "text": "You had no business being\nin Yellow Level, did you?",
    "start": 669.626,
    "duration": 3.42
  },
  {
    "text": "It was sabotage.",
    "start": 673.13,
    "duration": 1.251
  },
  {
    "text": "Sabotage, exactly. Jealousy, fear--",
    "start": 674.464,
    "duration": 2.086
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey, I faced the same obstacles.",
    "start": 676.633,
    "duration": 1.377
  },
  {
    "text": "In fact, you remind me a lot of myself\nwhen I was your age,",
    "start": 678.093,
    "duration": 5.214
  },
  {
    "text": "which is... now.",
    "start": 683.39,
    "duration": 3.128
  },
  {
    "text": "[groans, spits]",
    "start": 687.185,
    "duration": 1.877
  },
  {
    "text": "What?",
    "start": 690.063,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "[chuckles]",
    "start": 691.315,
    "duration": 1.376
  },
  {
    "text": "Surprise. Surprise.",
    "start": 692.774,
    "duration": 3.087
  },
  {
    "text": "What the frittata?",
    "start": 695.944,
    "duration": 2.461
  },
  {
    "text": "Well put.",
    "start": 698.488,
    "duration": 1.085
  },
  {
    "text": "He's a b-- You're a baby.",
    "start": 699.656,
    "duration": 2.294
  },
  {
    "text": "I repeat, you're a baby.",
    "start": 702.034,
    "duration": 2.669
  },
  {
    "text": "So surprised you said it twice. [chuckles]",
    "start": 704.786,
    "duration": 2.253
  },
  {
    "text": "[laughs]",
    "start": 707.122,
    "duration": 1.251
  },
  {
    "text": "Unfortunately, people are not ready",
    "start": 708.457,
    "duration": 2.961
  },
  {
    "text": "for a baby in a position of power... yet.",
    "start": 711.501,
    "duration": 4.255
  },
  {
    "text": "Remind me to get the number\nof your mutton chop guy.",
    "start": 716.34,
    "duration": 2.419
  },
  {
    "text": "You know, I could use somebody like you.",
    "start": 718.842,
    "duration": 2.92
  },
  {
    "text": "With a superior intelligence, like my own.",
    "start": 721.845,
    "duration": 3.629
  },
  {
    "text": "- Uh...\n- Mmm.",
    "start": 725.557,
    "duration": 1.085
  },
  {
    "text": "- Really?\n- Somebody who can, uh...",
    "start": 726.725,
    "duration": 2.419
  },
  {
    "text": "Mmm. [chews]",
    "start": 729.645,
    "duration": 2.168
  },
  {
    "text": "- [gasps]\n- Mmm. Yeah.",
    "start": 731.897,
    "duration": 1.376
  },
  {
    "text": "...truly comprehend\nwhat I'm trying to accomplish.",
    "start": 733.357,
    "duration": 3.086
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, you're looking at him.",
    "start": 736.526,
    "duration": 1.544
  },
  {
    "text": "Bingo. Mmm.",
    "start": 738.153,
    "duration": 1.293
  },
  {
    "text": "We have a secret level.\nFor very special babies.",
    "start": 739.988,
    "duration": 2.878
  },
  {
    "text": "Mmm. The best of the best. Ah, the elite.",
    "start": 742.949,
    "duration": 2.294
  },
  {
    "text": "Beyond blue?",
    "start": 745.327,
    "duration": 0.959
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, yeah. Way beyond.",
    "start": 746.37,
    "duration": 2.085
  },
  {
    "text": "Way beyond.",
    "start": 748.538,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "- [beeps]\n- [chimes]",
    "start": 749.956,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "There's a meeting today after school.",
    "start": 751.375,
    "duration": 2.836
  },
  {
    "text": "Babies only.",
    "start": 754.294,
    "duration": 1.376
  },
  {
    "text": "We may be small,",
    "start": 755.754,
    "duration": 1.209
  },
  {
    "text": "but we're about to teach grown-ups\na big lesson.",
    "start": 757.047,
    "duration": 3.879
  },
  {
    "text": "Lolly?",
    "start": 763.428,
    "duration": 1.126
  },
  {
    "text": "- Okay.\n- [school bell rings]",
    "start": 764.638,
    "duration": 1.126
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh. Time for recess.",
    "start": 765.847,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "Bye, bye.",
    "start": 767.265,
    "duration": 1.252
  },
  {
    "text": "Sayonara.",
    "start": 769.476,
    "duration": 2.085
  },
  {
    "text": "[grunts]",
    "start": 771.645,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "[grunts]",
    "start": 774.94,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "Well i think that went well.",
    "start": 776.066,
    "duration": 1.376
  },
  {
    "text": "- Quick, to the acorn!\n- Hyah!",
    "start": 777.943,
    "duration": 1.084
  },
  {
    "text": "[Tim grunts]",
    "start": 779.111,
    "duration": 1.084
  },
  {
    "text": "[both] Yee-haw!",
    "start": 781.53,
    "duration": 1.71
  },
  {
    "text": "Hold onto your chaps, pal.",
    "start": 783.323,
    "duration": 1.627
  },
  {
    "text": "- [baby ninja grunts]\n- Whoa!",
    "start": 785.033,
    "duration": 1.043
  },
  {
    "text": "[yells, grunts]",
    "start": 786.159,
    "duration": 1.919
  },
  {
    "text": "- [screams]\n- Oh, no!",
    "start": 791.623,
    "duration": 1.919
  },
  {
    "text": "Glue! [chuckles]",
    "start": 794.793,
    "duration": 2.002
  },
  {
    "text": "Yah! Pixie dust! [chuckles]",
    "start": 796.878,
    "duration": 2.544
  },
  {
    "text": "- Yeah, baby!\n- Yes!",
    "start": 799.506,
    "duration": 1.126
  },
  {
    "text": "[babbles]",
    "start": 800.715,
    "duration": 1.752
  },
  {
    "text": "[creepy girl chuckles]",
    "start": 803.135,
    "duration": 1.501
  },
  {
    "text": "[grunts]",
    "start": 805.47,
    "duration": 1.043
  },
  {
    "text": "[chuckles]",
    "start": 807.222,
    "duration": 1.251
  },
  {
    "text": "Wha--",
    "start": 809.057,
    "duration": 0.918
  },
  {
    "text": "[creepy girl, echoing]\nWhere'd I go?",
    "start": 810.058,
    "duration": 1.46
  },
  {
    "text": "- Whoa!\n- [chuckling] I like your pajamas.",
    "start": 813.103,
    "duration": 2.044
  },
  {
    "text": "[screams]",
    "start": 815.23,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "[ninjas crying]",
    "start": 817.274,
    "duration": 1.293
  },
  {
    "text": "[creepy girl] Where are you going?",
    "start": 819.651,
    "duration": 1.752
  },
  {
    "text": "- Hyah!\n- Whoo-hoo-hoo-hoo!",
    "start": 821.486,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "- Glue!\n- I'm proud to be a yellow.",
    "start": 822.904,
    "duration": 1.502
  },
  {
    "text": "- I like your pony.\n- [screams]",
    "start": 824.489,
    "duration": 2.336
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you.",
    "start": 826.908,
    "duration": 1.126
  },
  {
    "text": "- [crying, babbling]\n- [Erwin] What?",
    "start": 828.118,
    "duration": 2.044
  },
  {
    "text": "Huh, huh, huh. No, no, no.",
    "start": 830.245,
    "duration": 2.544
  },
  {
    "text": "Now let's crack that big nut. [grunts]",
    "start": 837.168,
    "duration": 2.628
  },
  {
    "text": "[Tim] Oh, no! It's about to go worldwide.",
    "start": 841.006,
    "duration": 2.377
  },
  {
    "text": "How are we gonna get up there?",
    "start": 843.466,
    "duration": 1.919
  },
  {
    "text": "- Really?\n- Well, you got grit.",
    "start": 846.72,
    "duration": 2.419
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll give ya that. Gumption, even.",
    "start": 849.222,
    "duration": 1.835
  },
  {
    "text": "Very admirable, and yet, annoying.",
    "start": 851.141,
    "duration": 3.003
  },
  {
    "text": "Quite annoying. Yeah.",
    "start": 854.227,
    "duration": 1.627
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm gonna have to, you know, stop you.",
    "start": 855.937,
    "duration": 2.962
  },
  {
    "text": "[Tim] Glue me, glue me.",
    "start": 858.982,
    "duration": 1.293
  },
  {
    "text": "- [Ted] Precious, sic 'em!\n- [blusters]",
    "start": 860.358,
    "duration": 1.293
  },
  {
    "text": "You're too little and too late.",
    "start": 861.735,
    "duration": 2.043
  },
  {
    "text": "- [bangs]\n- Ah! Bad-- Bad dog.",
    "start": 863.862,
    "duration": 1.96
  },
  {
    "text": "Pets aren't allowed in school.",
    "start": 865.906,
    "duration": 1.459
  },
  {
    "text": "Precious!",
    "start": 867.449,
    "duration": 1.501
  },
  {
    "text": "- And you, my pudgy protégé...\n- [Tim] Go, go, go! Move!",
    "start": 870.076,
    "duration": 2.962
  },
  {
    "text": "...I offered you the world.",
    "start": 873.121,
    "duration": 1.502
  },
  {
    "text": "- We could have been partners!\n- [Tim grunting]",
    "start": 874.706,
    "duration": 1.919
  },
  {
    "text": "I've got something better than a partner.",
    "start": 876.708,
    "duration": 1.793
  },
  {
    "text": "I have a brother.",
    "start": 878.585,
    "duration": 1.251
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah!",
    "start": 879.92,
    "duration": 1.334
  },
  {
    "text": "- Let go.\n- No, you let go.",
    "start": 881.338,
    "duration": 1.209
  },
  {
    "text": "Wow. Point taken.",
    "start": 882.631,
    "duration": 1.418
  },
  {
    "text": "- [loud bang]\n- What? What's going on?",
    "start": 884.132,
    "duration": 2.252
  },
  {
    "text": "[yells]",
    "start": 888.762,
    "duration": 1.167
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey, that's my leisure suit.",
    "start": 890.013,
    "duration": 1.293
  },
  {
    "text": "It looks better on her.",
    "start": 891.389,
    "duration": 1.293
  },
  {
    "text": "Hands up, diapers down.",
    "start": 892.766,
    "duration": 1.459
  },
  {
    "text": "Things are about to get weird.",
    "start": 894.309,
    "duration": 1.418
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah! That's my girls.",
    "start": 895.81,
    "duration": 1.502
  },
  {
    "text": "- That's really Dad?\n- Yep.",
    "start": 897.395,
    "duration": 1.961
  },
  {
    "text": "I said a lot of stuff to that kid.",
    "start": 899.439,
    "duration": 2.085
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, quite the family reunion.",
    "start": 901.608,
    "duration": 1.752
  },
  {
    "text": "Uh, the more the merrier.",
    "start": 903.443,
    "duration": 1.418
  },
  {
    "text": "- I say let's call your parents.\n- [Tim] Oh, no.",
    "start": 904.944,
    "duration": 2.586
  },
  {
    "text": "Uh-oh. Okay.",
    "start": 908.448,
    "duration": 1.627
  },
  {
    "text": "Mommy and Daddy, let's hug ‘em...",
    "start": 910.158,
    "duration": 1.71
  },
  {
    "text": "- to death.\n- Don't worry about us. Get to the server.",
    "start": 911.951,
    "duration": 2.461
  },
  {
    "text": "- Go, Tina, go!\n- Whoo!",
    "start": 914.496,
    "duration": 1.751
  },
  {
    "text": "- Uh... [stammers] Whoa!\n- [Tina yells]",
    "start": 917.707,
    "duration": 1.669
  },
  {
    "text": "- Hey!\n- [grunts] You got this, Tina.",
    "start": 919.459,
    "duration": 1.668
  },
  {
    "text": "Get down from there!",
    "start": 921.211,
    "duration": 1.501
  },
  {
    "text": "[Ted] Go for his lollies!",
    "start": 922.796,
    "duration": 1.543
  },
  {
    "text": "Never touch another man's pony!",
    "start": 924.422,
    "duration": 2.544
  },
  {
    "text": "- [muffled grunts]\n- Here, stick around. Stick around.",
    "start": 927.05,
    "duration": 3.462
  },
  {
    "text": "Uh, Tim, what do we do now?",
    "start": 930.595,
    "duration": 2.211
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't move! Maybe they won't see us.",
    "start": 932.889,
    "duration": 1.794
  },
  {
    "text": "They see us, Tim. They see us!",
    "start": 934.766,
    "duration": 1.501
  },
  {
    "text": "- Did you move? I didn't move.\n- Really, Tim?",
    "start": 936.351,
    "duration": 2.127
  },
  {
    "text": "- [Tabitha] That's a little too high now.\n- Don't look down.",
    "start": 939.479,
    "duration": 2.169
  },
  {
    "text": "- Look straight ahead, okay?\n- [whimpers] Oh.",
    "start": 941.731,
    "duration": 2.878
  },
  {
    "text": "- [buzzes]\n- It's locked.",
    "start": 945.443,
    "duration": 1.71
  },
  {
    "text": "Can I give you a hand?",
    "start": 947.237,
    "duration": 1.626
  },
  {
    "text": "Of course, I mean that facetiously\nbecause the hand acts as a key.",
    "start": 948.947,
    "duration": 4.004
  },
  {
    "text": "No, no, no!",
    "start": 953.034,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "- Hey! No! No!\n- Thanks, sis.",
    "start": 954.119,
    "duration": 1.876
  },
  {
    "text": "[grunts] Stay away from my server.",
    "start": 956.079,
    "duration": 1.71
  },
  {
    "text": "[yells]",
    "start": 957.872,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "- [Tina] Shut it down, Tabitha!\n- What are you doing?",
    "start": 959.29,
    "duration": 1.919
  },
  {
    "text": "No, no! No! Don't do that.",
    "start": 961.292,
    "duration": 3.504
  },
  {
    "text": "- [Tim] Oh, no!\n- Hug Grandpa.",
    "start": 965.088,
    "duration": 2.294
  },
  {
    "text": "- It's night of the living boomers.\n- [Carol] Hugs.",
    "start": 967.465,
    "duration": 2.169
  },
  {
    "text": "- Dad, stop!\n- Hug.",
    "start": 969.717,
    "duration": 1.377
  },
  {
    "text": "[screams]",
    "start": 971.177,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "- [screams]\n- [grunts]",
    "start": 972.595,
    "duration": 1.418
  },
  {
    "text": "[gasps]",
    "start": 974.097,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "Back! Back, you little monsters.",
    "start": 975.181,
    "duration": 2.127
  },
  {
    "text": "- You back off, candy pants.\n- [grunts]",
    "start": 977.392,
    "duration": 2.21
  },
  {
    "text": "- [yelps]\n- Got your nose!",
    "start": 980.395,
    "duration": 2.502
  },
  {
    "text": "Aw, right in the breadbasket!",
    "start": 983.815,
    "duration": 2.127
  },
  {
    "text": "[both grunting]",
    "start": 986.985,
    "duration": 1.918
  },
  {
    "text": "[both grunting]",
    "start": 988.987,
    "duration": 2.46
  },
  {
    "text": "- Knocked his block off!\n- Ah, poopy.",
    "start": 995.535,
    "duration": 1.543
  },
  {
    "text": "Tina, I think I got it. Yes!",
    "start": 997.162,
    "duration": 1.96
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't hit that button.\nDon't hit that button.",
    "start": 999.205,
    "duration": 1.752
  },
  {
    "text": "And... enter.",
    "start": 1003.042,
    "duration": 1.71
  },
  {
    "text": "No, no. Stop it. Cut it out.",
    "start": 1004.836,
    "duration": 2.336
  },
  {
    "text": "- Look what you made me do.\n- [gasps]",
    "start": 1007.255,
    "duration": 1.501
  },
  {
    "text": "The fire alarm.",
    "start": 1009.424,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "Ah! Darn it.",
    "start": 1010.508,
    "duration": 1.085
  },
  {
    "text": "Dad! Uncle Ted!",
    "start": 1011.676,
    "duration": 1.585
  },
  {
    "text": "Pull the fire alarm!",
    "start": 1013.344,
    "duration": 1.252
  },
  {
    "text": "- The girls need help.\n- No kissies!",
    "start": 1014.679,
    "duration": 1.418
  },
  {
    "text": "The girls need us.",
    "start": 1016.181,
    "duration": 2.335
  },
  {
    "text": "- [bell rings]\n- [grunts] Time's up, halflings.",
    "start": 1018.6,
    "duration": 2.669
  },
  {
    "text": "[grunts] Great galloping gargoyles!",
    "start": 1021.895,
    "duration": 2.502
  },
  {
    "text": "What? Where-- What?",
    "start": 1025.19,
    "duration": 1.71
  },
  {
    "text": "[screams]",
    "start": 1026.983,
    "duration": 1.084
  },
  {
    "text": "Tim! Get to the fire alarm!",
    "start": 1028.151,
    "duration": 2.127
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll hold them back.",
    "start": 1030.361,
    "duration": 1.293
  },
  {
    "text": "[Ted] Make it rain, baby!",
    "start": 1031.738,
    "duration": 2.002
  },
  {
    "text": "- [Tim] I'm on it.\n- What's the matter?",
    "start": 1033.823,
    "duration": 2.211
  },
  {
    "text": "You can't handle the awkward phase?",
    "start": 1036.117,
    "duration": 2.086
  },
  {
    "text": "[whimpers]",
    "start": 1038.286,
    "duration": 1.084
  },
  {
    "text": "Go, Marcos!",
    "start": 1039.454,
    "duration": 1.042
  },
  {
    "text": "Dad, go!",
    "start": 1040.58,
    "duration": 1.043
  },
  {
    "text": "- [gasps]\n- I'm back!",
    "start": 1041.706,
    "duration": 1.501
  },
  {
    "text": "- Here we go!\n- Come on.",
    "start": 1043.291,
    "duration": 1.376
  },
  {
    "text": "How about another round, ya tough guy?\nCome on!",
    "start": 1044.751,
    "duration": 2.294
  },
  {
    "text": "Stop it!",
    "start": 1047.128,
    "duration": 1.21
  },
  {
    "text": "I still got these. [grunting]",
    "start": 1048.421,
    "duration": 1.502
  },
  {
    "text": "[Tabitha] You put my sister down!",
    "start": 1050.006,
    "duration": 1.293
  },
  {
    "text": "B-Day will happen,\nwhether you like it or not.",
    "start": 1051.382,
    "duration": 3.295
  },
  {
    "text": "You shall not pass!",
    "start": 1054.761,
    "duration": 1.96
  },
  {
    "text": "You shall not pass.",
    "start": 1057.305,
    "duration": 1.543
  },
  {
    "text": "No! Stop passing.",
    "start": 1058.932,
    "duration": 1.626
  },
  {
    "text": "- [grunts]\n- [alarm blares]",
    "start": 1060.642,
    "duration": 1.584
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, Dad! Way to go! Whoo!",
    "start": 1063.061,
    "duration": 1.751
  },
  {
    "text": "[alarm stops]",
    "start": 1065.396,
    "duration": 0.96
  },
  {
    "text": "[Tabitha gasps] That's it?",
    "start": 1066.439,
    "duration": 2.294
  },
  {
    "text": "That's right. Why, what?",
    "start": 1068.816,
    "duration": 1.377
  },
  {
    "text": "The school's expensive.\nI had to cut costs someplace.",
    "start": 1070.276,
    "duration": 2.628
  },
  {
    "text": "- [thud]\n- [both grunt]",
    "start": 1072.987,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "- Oh, no. It's not working.\n- Did you pull it right?",
    "start": 1074.072,
    "duration": 2.043
  },
  {
    "text": "How else you gonna pull it?",
    "start": 1076.199,
    "duration": 1.418
  },
  {
    "text": "[chuckles]\nYou'll see I'm right. I'll show everybody.",
    "start": 1077.7,
    "duration": 3.712
  },
  {
    "text": "The age of parents is over.",
    "start": 1081.496,
    "duration": 3.086
  },
  {
    "text": "[babbling]",
    "start": 1084.666,
    "duration": 2.21
  },
  {
    "text": "[Erwin] Yay, yay, yay.",
    "start": 1089.504,
    "duration": 2.002
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, how about you watch me\nhave a little toast.",
    "start": 1091.589,
    "duration": 3.087
  },
  {
    "text": "To the baby revolution, and to me.",
    "start": 1094.759,
    "duration": 3.003
  },
  {
    "text": "[gasps]",
    "start": 1097.845,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "It's time for the candy volcano...",
    "start": 1101.516,
    "duration": 1.877
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, that's good.",
    "start": 1103.476,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "- [both] ...of doom!\n- What are you doing?",
    "start": 1104.56,
    "duration": 1.627
  },
  {
    "text": "What are you doing? No, no! No!",
    "start": 1106.27,
    "duration": 2.586
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, no, no, no!",
    "start": 1108.94,
    "duration": 2.335
  },
  {
    "text": "- No, no!\n- Boomshakalaka?",
    "start": 1111.359,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "- Boom!\n- Don't do that!",
    "start": 1112.443,
    "duration": 2.294
  },
  {
    "text": "[screaming]",
    "start": 1114.821,
    "duration": 1.71
  },
  {
    "text": "[Ted] Whoa!",
    "start": 1119.242,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, no! Tabitha.",
    "start": 1122.328,
    "duration": 1.543
  },
  {
    "text": "No! Someone help me, please!",
    "start": 1125.748,
    "duration": 2.002
  },
  {
    "text": "Tabitha. Hang on!",
    "start": 1127.834,
    "duration": 1.626
  },
  {
    "text": "Ted, I need upsies. Now!",
    "start": 1129.544,
    "duration": 2.085
  },
  {
    "text": "[Ted grunts]",
    "start": 1131.713,
    "duration": 1.793
  },
  {
    "text": "Dad, help me!",
    "start": 1138.261,
    "duration": 1.543
  },
  {
    "text": "Look at you.\nYou're smart. You're strong.",
    "start": 1139.887,
    "duration": 2.92
  },
  {
    "text": "You don't need parents.",
    "start": 1142.89,
    "duration": 1.418
  },
  {
    "text": "What can they possibly offer you?",
    "start": 1144.392,
    "duration": 2.21
  },
  {
    "text": "- How about unconditional love?\n- Ah!",
    "start": 1146.686,
    "duration": 2.21
  },
  {
    "text": "- [Tina] That's what.\n- No, no.",
    "start": 1148.98,
    "duration": 1.585
  },
  {
    "text": "- Sayonaral!\n- No!",
    "start": 1150.648,
    "duration": 1.877
  },
  {
    "text": "- [whimpers]\n- [Tim] Tabitha!",
    "start": 1156.737,
    "duration": 1.585
  },
  {
    "text": "[Tabitha grunting]",
    "start": 1158.406,
    "duration": 1.668
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm gonna fall!",
    "start": 1161.534,
    "duration": 1.251
  },
  {
    "text": "Tabitha! Hang on!",
    "start": 1162.869,
    "duration": 2.002
  },
  {
    "text": "[screaming]",
    "start": 1164.954,
    "duration": 1.376
  },
  {
    "text": "I gotcha! I gotcha!",
    "start": 1166.914,
    "duration": 1.627
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh! I gotcha, Tabitha.",
    "start": 1169.5,
    "duration": 2.419
  },
  {
    "text": "[both breathing heavily]",
    "start": 1172.003,
    "duration": 1.543
  },
  {
    "text": "I gotcha.",
    "start": 1175.923,
    "duration": 1.418
  },
  {
    "text": "That's my big brother.",
    "start": 1177.925,
    "duration": 1.21
  }
]